text: Egobunma "Ego" Nwodim (; born March 10, 1988) is an American actress and comedian. She is a featured player on the forty-fourth season of Saturday Night Live. She starred in supporting roles on television for Nwodim include Law & Order True Crime: The Menendez Murders (a three-episode arc in 2017), 2 Broke Girls, and Living Biblically. ==References== ==Other websites== * *Upright Citizens Brigade page Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Actors from Baltimore Category:Comedians from Baltimore
